data.description: ADORABLE Single story Gem, just 7 minutes from the Mission Inn and Downtown Riverside. 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, 1400 sq feet. Spacious living room, cute kitchen. Large family room overlooks pool and backyard. Two car attached garage. Large driveway with RV parking. Newer roof and windows for modern comfort and style. Easy access to the 215 and 91 freeway. Close to University of Riverside and Riverside Community Hospital. Quite well maintained family oriented neighborhood.
